  p.
    Card images can have #[code .card__image--left] or #[code .card__image--right]. This changes the flexbox order of the image.
    
  p.
    However, if your card image spans the whole width of the card, then you don't need these modifier classes.
  
  h3 Horizontal or Vertical Layouts

  p.
    By default, cards display their main content (the image and the body) arranged horizontally, as columns. But if your card image is wide enough, or if the card width constrained narrow enough, then the 'columns' wrap to become 'rows' and you get the traditional card layout.
    
