          +paragraph(4)
        .card__footer
          | Footer
      
  p.
    #[b Note:] #[code .card__section] does not have this same behavior.  

  h3 Cards can be Nested
    
  p.
    There may be some circumstances where you need to "nest" cards &ndash; or place smaller card(s) "over" a bigger card. As Codebase cards are media objects, you would expect to be able to do this and you can, easily. 
  
